document.full_text: a series of unsealed 1960s audio recordings of jacqueline kennedy talking about her life with husband and revered president john f. kennedy will be broadcast on television, abc news said on wednesday.
document.title: unsealed jackie kennedy interviews to air on tv
lines_and_colors: a series of unsealed 1960s audio recordings of jacqueline kennedy talking about her life with husband and revered president john f. kennedy will be broadcast on television, abc news said on wednesday.
